## 為什麼需要 Streams
```javascript
// ❌ 整檔讀進記憶體—100GB 直接爆
const data = await fs.readFile("huge.csv");

// ✅ Stream—逐行處理、記憶體只用幾 MB
import { createReadStream } from "node:fs";
import readline from "node:readline";

const rl = readline.createInterface({
  input: createReadStream("huge.csv"),
});

for await (const line of rl) {
  // 處理每一行
}
```

## 三大 stream 類型

### Readable（讀取源）
```javascript
import { createReadStream } from "node:fs";

const stream = createReadStream("data.txt", { encoding: "utf-8" });
stream.on("data", chunk => console.log("got chunk:", chunk.length));
stream.on("end", () => console.log("done"));
stream.on("error", err => console.error(err));
```

### Writable（寫入目的地）
```javascript
import { createWriteStream } from "node:fs";

const out = createWriteStream("output.txt");
out.write("hello\n");
out.write("world\n");
out.end();  // 結束
```

### Transform（讀取 → 處理 → 寫出）
```javascript
import { Transform } from "node:stream";
import { pipeline } from "node:stream/promises";
import { createReadStream, createWriteStream } from "node:fs";
import { createGzip } from "node:zlib";

await pipeline(
  createReadStream("huge.txt"),
  createGzip(),                    // gzip 壓縮
  createWriteStream("huge.txt.gz")
);
```

## CSV 處理範例
```javascript
import { Transform } from "node:stream";
import { pipeline } from "node:stream/promises";
import csv from "csv-parser";

const filter = new Transform({
  objectMode: true,
  transform(row, enc, cb) {
    if (Number(row.age) >= 18) this.push(row);
    cb();
  },
});

const toCsv = new Transform({
  objectMode: true,
  transform(row, enc, cb) {
    cb(null, `${row.name},${row.age}\n`);
  },
});

await pipeline(
  createReadStream("input.csv"),
  csv(),
  filter,
  toCsv,
  createWriteStream("adults.csv")
);
```

## Web Streams API（跨平台、現代）
```javascript
const res = await fetch("https://example.com/big.json");
const reader = res.body!.getReader();
const decoder = new TextDecoder();

while (true) {
  const { done, value } = await reader.read();
  if (done) break;
  console.log(decoder.decode(value));
}
```

